</li>
<li sourcefile="V1/Installation/Install OSIsoft Adapter for DNP3 using Docker.md" sourcestartlinenumber="136" sourceendlinenumber="136"><p sourcefile="V1/Installation/Install OSIsoft Adapter for DNP3 using Docker.md" sourcestartlinenumber="136" sourceendlinenumber="136">Name the script <em>dnp3dockerstart.sh</em> and save it to the directory where you plan to create the container.</p>
</li>
